        <div class=WordSection1>

            <p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:center;
line-height:normal'><b><u>PRICING POLICY</u></b></p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal'><span
                    style='font-family:Wingdings'>v<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;
            </span></span>At Sandesh, we offer the “SENDER” the cheapest and the most
                competitive courier charges for shipping their parcels as well as an
                opportunity for the “TRAVELER” to earn from each of his/her journey by offering
                his/her service for delivering the parcels.</p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:normal'>&nbsp;</p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal'><span
                    style='font-family:Wingdings'>v<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;
            </span></span>The pricing of the Courier Services / Delivery Charges of the parcels
                are being calculated on the following two parameters;</p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;
margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:76.5pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-family:Wingdings'>v<span
                    style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp; </span></span>Actual weight or
                volumetric weight of the parcel, and</p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;
margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:76.5pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-family:Wingdings'>v<span
                    style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp; </span></span>Delivery terms</p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpLast style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;
margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:76.5pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
line-height:normal'>&nbsp;</p>

            <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:normal'><b><u>Process of finalization of weight of
                the consignment</u></b></p>

            <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:normal'><b><u><span style='text-decoration:none'>&nbsp;</span></u></b></p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal'><span
                    style='font-family:Wingdings'>v<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;
            </span></span>“Actual weight” of the parcel is defined as<i>“the weight of the
                goods being shipped along with its protective materials and boxes / cartons in
                which it is being packed along with the weight of the bags / packing in which
                it is handed over to the traveler”.</i></p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:normal'>&nbsp;</p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal'><span
                    style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;color:black'>v<span
                    style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp; </span></span><span
                    style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;color:black'>“Volumetric
                Weight or Dimensional Weight” of the parcel is defined as the volume of space a
                parcel occupies during travel / distribution / delivery and is </span>calculated
                by assessing the physical dimension of the parcel i.e. Length, Breadth and
                Height of the parcel (size of the packet after final packing). The volumetric
                weight is calculated as under;</p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpLast style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;color:black'>&nbsp;</span></p>

            <p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:center;
line-height:normal'><u><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;
color:black'>Length x Breadth x Height (in cms)</span></u><span
                    style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;color:black'><br>
                5000</span></p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst><span style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
115%;font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;color:black;background:yellow'>&nbsp;</span></p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpLast style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal'><span
                    style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;color:black'>v<span
                    style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp; </span></span><span
                    style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;color:black'>The calculation
                of shipment cost is based on “Actual Weight” &amp; “Volumetric or Dimensional
                weight” of a shipment. The volumetric or dimensional weight is calculated and
                compared with the actual weight of the shipment to ascertain which is greater. Higher
                of the two weightsis used to calculate the shipment cost.</span></p>

            <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;color:black'>&nbsp;</span></p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal'><span
                    style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;color:black'>v<span
                    style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp; </span></span><span
                    style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;color:black'>If
                any dimension of the Consignments exceeds 110cms then 2 times the weight (Gross
                or Volumetric, whichever is more) is directly charged to the sender.</span></p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;color:black'>&nbsp;</span></p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal'><span
                    style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;color:black'>v<span
                    style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp; </span></span><span
                    style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;color:black'>However,
                no provision for calculation of shipping cost to SENDER in terms of volumetric
                weight is available in the application. As such, it shall be <b><u>TRAVELER’s
                    responsibility</u></b> to calculate the volumetric weight of the consignment
                and select appropriate weight bracket for actual calculation of pricing. In
                this regard, actual weight of the consignment or volumetric weight of the
                consignment, whichever is higher will be considered for actual pricing and <b><u>SENDER
                    shall be required to pay the </u></b></span>cost<b><u><span style='font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;color:black'> as per weight bracket
                finalized by TRAVELER.</span></u></b></p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;color:black'>&nbsp;</span></p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal'><span
                    style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;color:black'>v<span
                    style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp; </span></span><span
                    style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;color:black'>It
                shall be sender’s responsibility to provide adequate proof with regard to
                weight of the Consignments. In case of dispute in weight, the sender to arrange
                for weighing scale and finalize the weight in agreement with traveler. </span></p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;color:black'>&nbsp;</span></p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpLast style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal'><span
                    style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;color:black'>v<span
                    style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp; </span></span><b><u><span
                    style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;color:black'>The
                weight bracket finalized by TRAVELER at the time of start journey shall be the
                final and no modifications / disputes by any parties with regard to weight
                shall be entertained thereafter.</span></u></b><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;color:black'><br>
                <br>
            </span></p>

            <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:normal'><b><u><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;color:black'><span style='text-decoration:
 none'>&nbsp;</span></span></u></b></p>

            <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:normal'><b><u><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;color:black'>Process of finalization of
                Delivery Terms</span></u></b></p>

            <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:normal'><b><u><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;color:black'><span style='text-decoration:
 none'>&nbsp;</span></span></u></b></p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal'><span
                    style='font-family:Wingdings'>v<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;
            </span></span>The delivery term is the other criteria for calculation of cost
                of shipping for the senders. We provide following four types of delivery
                services to the senders;</p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal'><span
                    style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;color:black'>v<span
                    style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp; </span></span><b><u><span
                    style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;color:black'>Door
                to Door Service (Higher charges)- </span></u></b><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;color:black'>Traveler shall pick up the
                Consignments from Sender’s Place (Door pick up) and shall arrange for delivery
                of the Consignments at Receiver’s place (Door delivery).</span></p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:normal'><b><u><span style='font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;color:black'><span
                    style='text-decoration:none'>&nbsp;</span></span></u></b></p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal'><span
                    style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;color:black'>v<span
                    style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp; </span></span><b><u><span
                    style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;color:black'>Traveler’s
                place to Traveler’s place (Common Point pick up to Common Point delivery –
                Lowest charges): </span></u></b><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;
color:black'>Sender shall arrange for handing over the Consignments to Traveler
                at the Pick-up Point (Common Point pick up) as per mutually agreed terms
                between Sender and Traveler. The sender/Receiver shall arrange for taking
                delivery of the Consignments from traveler’s place (Common Point delivery).</span></p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:normal'><b><u><span style='font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;color:black'><span
                    style='text-decoration:none'>&nbsp;</span></span></u></b></p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal'><span
                    style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;color:black'>v<span
                    style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp; </span></span><b><u><span
                    style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;color:black'>Sender’s
                place to Traveler’s place (Door pick up to Common Point delivery – Medium
                charges) - </span></u></b><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;
color:black'>Traveler shall pick up the Consignments from Sender’s Place (Door
                pick up) and the Consignments shall be picked up by Receiver from the Traveler’s
                place which can be Traveler’s house or Railway Station or Bus Stand or any
                other point proposed by Traveler (Common Point).</span></p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:normal'><b><u><span style='font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;color:black'><span
                    style='text-decoration:none'>&nbsp;</span></span></u></b></p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpLast style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal'><span
                    style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;color:black'>v<span
                    style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp; </span></span><b><u><span
                    style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;color:black'>Traveler’s
                place to Receiver’s place (Common Point pick up to Door delivery) – Medium
                charges): </span></u></b><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;
color:black'>Sender shall arrange for handing over the Consignments to Traveler
                at the Pick-up Point (Common Point) as per mutually agreed terms between Sender
                and Traveler.Traveler shall deliver the consignment to the Receiver’s place
                (Door Delivery).</span></p>

            <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:normal'><b><u><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:"Trebuchet MS",sans-serif;color:black'><span style='text-decoration:
 none'>&nbsp;</span></span></u></b></p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal'><span
                    style='font-family:Wingdings'>v<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;
            </span></span>The “SANDESH” app provides an option to both the senders and
                travelers to propose their preferences in terms of delivery mode by selecting
                any of these above four delivery terms while entering “Send Parcel – for
                Sender” and Plan a Travel – for Traveler”. </p>

            <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:normal'>&nbsp;</p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal'><span
                    style='font-family:Wingdings'>v<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;
            </span></span>Based on the circumstances and preferences, the senders and
                travelers shall submit their requests to other parties to enter into a
                transaction. Both the sender and traveler are required to discuss and finalize
                a delivery term based upon their preferences before proceeding for any journey
                either by Traveler or Sender. Any of the two parties are at freedom to cancel
                the contract if delivery terms are not agreed upon but only till the time any
                of the parties start proceeding for pick up of parcel. The company shall not
                entertain any claim or dispute with regard to expenses or losses incurred by
                any parties in this regard.</p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:normal'>&nbsp;</p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal'><span
                    style='font-family:Wingdings'>v<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;
            </span></span>At the time of Start Journey by “TRAVELER”, it is the
                responsibility of the Traveler to physically verify the “Actual Weight” or the “Volumetric
                Weight” of the parcel and get the same tallied with the weight entered by the
                Sender in the App. Further Traveler shall also verify the delivery terms
                entered by the Sender in the App. Finalization with regard to weight and
                Delivery Terms shall be the responsibility of the Traveler.</p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle>&nbsp;</p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal'><span
                    style='font-family:Wingdings'>v<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;
            </span></span>In case of any modification required with regard to weight or
                delivery terms, the Traveler to reject the order by citing proper reason and
                suggesting for modification. The Sender shall then modify his Send Parcel
                details and shall search for Traveler and will resend the request to traveler
                who will again check the details and shall then accept the order and proceed
                with “Start Journey”. </p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-bottom:0in;line-height:normal'>&nbsp;</p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal'><span
                    style='font-family:Wingdings'>v<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;
            </span></span>Applicable Service Charges towards the courier service shall be
                recovered from Sender and Service charges shall be paid to the Traveler through
                our app based payment system only based on the final data submitted at the time
                of start journey and no claims whatsoever shall be entertained thereafter. </p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-bottom:0in;line-height:normal'>&nbsp;</p>

            <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpLast style='margin-bottom:0in;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal'><span
                    style='font-family:Wingdings'>v<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;
            </span></span>Also by undertaking the services for the App, both the Senders
                and Travelers agree to pay or allow the company to deduct any cost or charges
                whatsoever for the delayed services or towards any statutory dues / applicable
                taxes / charges / extra charges etc as mentioned in the Terms and Conditions.</p>

